The following companies had unusual
price changes in Mexico trading. Stock symbols are in
parentheses and prices are as of 4 p.m. New York time.  The IPC index gained 0.6 percent to 35,678.92.  Empresas ICA SAB (ICA* MM), the countryâ€™s biggest
construction company, advanced 1.2 percent to 28.28 pesos. ICA
would consider offers to sell its airport unit, Chief Financial
Officer Alonso Quintana said in an e-mailed response to
questions.  Grupo Aeroportuario del Centro Norte SAB (OMAB MM) rose 1.7
